name: Manager Anny ft. Venus Beach Juice
description:
Anny: Ohh! ¡Hola! I’m Anny, manager of this bodega.
Anny: And I see you already met Ónix.. crazy cat! 
Anny: I’ll be there with you in a minute. Lemme just put this juices on the fridge. Have you tried this new brand? It’s called Venus Beach a secret recipe by La Peligrosa. They’re DELICIOUS and magical ⭐️ I’ll save you one. Please, feel free to look around while it cools :D
